li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a &lt;strong data-start="314" data-end="338"&gt;standalone armor set&lt;/strong&gt; that works on Link’s &lt;strong data-start="360" data-end="383"&gt;original model. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully upgradeable and dyeable!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Each piece can be freely mixed with other armor sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Compatible with both default animations and female animation mods.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Design: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The armor set is based off Zelda's model, Yamato's hair (One Piece), Zonai and Dragon Armor, and Master Sword concept art. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Upgrades&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 1 (Light Dragon): Gloom resistance + Zonai efficiency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 2 (Naydra): Cold resistance + Ice attack charge power&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 3 (Dinraal): Hot and Flame resistance + Fire charge attack power&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 4 (Farosh): Lightning resistance + Lightning immunity + Lightning attack charge power&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Light Dragon Master Sword:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Standalone master sword, base dmg 60, durability x3, and heal on hit&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master Sword cutscene uses the new Light Dragon model&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Location:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Armor and sword can be obtained in &lt;strong data-start="1166" data-end="1189"&gt;Zelda’s Secret Well&lt;/strong&gt; (Hateno Village)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Optional:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2173" data-end="2187"&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/523154"&gt;Femme Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (female voice mod) — by &lt;em data-start="2212" data-end="2225"&gt;SpaceGeorge &amp; &lt;/em&gt;Adeline Chetail&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2230" data-end="2245"&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/469131"&gt;Femboy Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (female animation mod) — by &lt;em data-start="2274" data-end="2288"&gt;Lord Bubbles&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/wips/84300"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dark Zonai Tech&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (Zonai retexture mod) — by Aster&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Artist Credits:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2313" data-end="2325" class="SelectedElement"&gt;RaiOuArt (‪&lt;a href="https://bsky.app/profile/raiouart.bsky.social"&gt;Bluesky&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href="https://x.com/RaiOuArt"&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)‬&lt;/strong&gt; — Original concept artwork for the Light Dragon Master Sword&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2391" data-end="2402"&gt;ilham45&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;em data-start="2405" data-end="2425"&gt;Yamato (One Piece)&lt;/em&gt; 3D model (hair mesh and textures adapted for this mod)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
