      <guid isPermaLink="false">d415efb5362c4864771aaac464b2439e59528321</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Jul 2025 03:54:26 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/685af92c23c19.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6875219bd80b8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686f474946d89.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/685b69e194393.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6872cf18abbdb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6872cf18aef3d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6872cf18d6cb0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/688995ae46be6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/685af932054b3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Size refinements&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Manual refinements to some previously oversized Lightroots - see the map picture in the gallery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Despite all sizes being set to 0.5 previously, the distribution of Lightroots and how the system works means that some wound up being far bigger than others, creating large regions of fully lit Depths, mostly around the edges. Those have been hand tweaked to make them more consistent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vanilla+ version cleared up some regions that still had too much Y-fog, which can look very strange when mixed with the added darkness of this mod.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Restore darkness, challenge and mystery to the Depths.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Reduced radius of effect of all lightroots, retaining large regions of the original pitch blackness, even with every lightroot lit.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The light effect of the lightroots is linked to the reveal of the map by the game code, so for now if you want darkness to reign, you lose the map too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I intend to release an update fine-tuning the area effect size per lightroot to optimise for gameplay.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As of v1.0.1, now a version with fine-tuned Vanilla+ biomes by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/4281118"&gt;WarioSnap &lt;/a&gt;(for use with &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/578624"&gt;Depths of the Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/605379"&gt;Hyrule Rebeautified&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Enjoy! Don't forget to pack brightbloom seeds.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;Recommended to install with TKMM, as this edits the Bootup file.&lt;/b&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/darkness_reigns_v11_with_vanilla_biomes_fog_correction.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/darkness_reigns_v11.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/darkness_reigns_v10_with_vanilla_biomes_fog_correction.zip" type="application/zip"/>
